text: Headstart with Karen Davila is a Philippine morning news and talk show broadcast by the ABS-CBN News Channel (ANC), hosted by Karen Davila. It premiered on March 1, 2010 and airs Monday to Friday at 08:00 (PST). == Host == * Karen Davila == Segment == * Hot Copy == References == Category:ABS-CBN News Channel original programming Category:Philippine television talk shows Category:2010 Philippine television series debuts Category:English-language television shows
